        "timestamp": "2018-09-07 11:40:07.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1\n\n(16 comments)\n\nI have seen a progress in your code. This version of DC have not got implementation for loading configuration in cloud environment(from consul, confingBindingService). We have got this implementation in the newest version of prh, please take a look.\n\nYou have mixed from reactive and imperative \"style\" http client. So I don't guarantee that it works. We have spent a lot of time in connection with understanding the reactive way and even then we had a lot of mistakes/bugs.\n\nFor now I can't give you +1. If you correct our comments and upgrade some code with the newest prh, it will be a pleasure",
